-- Yemen’s Acting Leader Hadi May Leave Capital, Jazeera Reports
-- B y   Z a i d   S a b a h
-- 2012-01-07T16:17:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-07/yemen-s-acting-leader-hadi-may-leave-capital-jazeera-reports.html
Yemen’s acting leader Abdurabuh
Mansur Hadi said he would leave the capital, Sana’a, if outgoing
president Ali Abdullah Saleh interferes with his role,  Al
Jazeera  reported, without saying where it got the information.  A new Yemeni government was sworn in last month after Saleh
agreed to relinquish presidential powers.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zaid Sabah Abd Alhamid in Washington at 
 zalhamid@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will Daley at 
 wdaley2@bloomberg.net  